        <div class="col-md-3">
            <p class = "lead">YelpCamp</p>
            <div class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item active">Info 1</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Info 2</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Info 3</li>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <div class="thumbnail">
                <img class="image-responsive" src="<%= campground.image %>">
                <div class="caption-full caption">
                    <p class="pull-right">$9.00/night</p>
                    <h4><a href="#"><%= campground.name %></a></h4>
                    <!-- <p><%= campground.description %></p> -->
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quae velit iste labore nostrum tenetur et consectetur corporis fuga atque, at, quaerat veritatis vitae ullam. Tenetur hic cum natus provident sequi.
                    Blanditiis beatae, in, quos tenetur ad asperiores iste corporis recusandae saepe repudiandae vitae iure dicta animi eum. Fugiat dignissimos, sequi dolores ullam quidem aspernatur illo sunt nulla numquam ea saepe.
